---
import Layout from "../layout.astro"
import {Image} from "astro:assets"
import anime from "../hex4-anime-alt.png"
---

<Layout title="hex4@net:~">
	
	<div class="w-screen h-8 px-2 py-1 flex">
		<span class="font-bold text-peach motion-preset-slide-up motion-delay-100">hex4</span>
		<span class="mx-3 text-surface2 motion-preset-slide-up motion-delay-200"> @ </span>
		<span class="motion-preset-slide-up font-bold text-yellow motion-delay-300">internet</span>
		<span class=" text-surface2 motion-preset-slide-up motion-delay-300"> : </span>
		<span class="text-text motion-preset-slide-up motion-delay-[400ms] mx-3">~</span>
		<span class="grow"></span>
		<span></span>
		<span class="mx-3 text-surface2 motion-preset-slide-right motion-delay-200 hover:text-text hover:font-bold transition-all">~</span>
		<span class="mx-3 text-surface2 motion-preset-slide-right motion-delay-200 hover:text-text hover:font-bold transition-all">about</span>
		<span class="mx-3 text-surface2 motion-preset-slide-right motion-delay-200 hover:text-text hover:font-bold transition-all">blog</span>
		<span class="mx-3 text-surface2 motion-preset-slide-right motion-delay-200 hover:text-text hover:font-bold transition-all ">projects</span>
	</div>
	<div class="px-10 pt-5 ">
		<div class="w-screen my-3 flex flex-row motion-delay-100 motion-preset-blur-right ">
			<img src={anime.src} alt="hex4 word with icons around, looks very cool" class="w-64">
			<div class="h-2 ml-4 bg-gradient-to-r grow my-auto from-red via-yellow to-blue rounded-full"></div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="motion-preset-blur-right motion-delay-300">
			<p class="text-text whitespace-pre-line w-3/4">oh, hey there. welcome to my lil corner of the internet!

				I'm hex4, a web dev, game dev, designer... lots of stuff. I guess you could call me a creative technologist? idk.

				The web these days feels boring. It feels like it's all the same. Sure, there's a ton of creativity out there, but it's stuck on a <a class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-wavy  transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:text-blue" href="https://x.com">few</a> <a class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-wavy  transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:text-red" href="https://youtube.com">huge</a> <a class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-wavy  transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:text-peach" href="https://reddit.com">websites</a>, forced to mold to those businesses' growth goals.

				I'm trying to bring back the old net, the time where people made toys, games, blogs and so, so, so much more. They didn't care about revenue, or likes, or upvotes. They just made things, <i>because they <b>could.</b></i>

				that's my mission. that's why I'm here.

				to make the web fun again!

				see ya around.

				more about me: <a href="about" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-wavy  transition-all hover:font-extrabold hover:text-peach">cd ./about</a>

				
			</p>

			<div class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r h-[2px] from-red via-peach to-blue my-5"></div>
		</div>

	</div>


</Layout>

